title: Christian Dior Small ABCDior
description: Christian Dior small My Lady ABCDior bag in light pink lambskin leather with Cannage stitching. Featuring light gold-tone hardware, including Dior letter charms. The leather flap top opens to a brown textile-lined interior with a patch pocket and a zip pocket. Approximate dimensions: 20cm(L) x 18cm(H) x 8cm(D), 8cm handle drop, 44cm strap drop with charms. Accompanied by Dior authentication card (dated 06/2019) and information booklet. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
